{"tid":2479220,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[4月新番] 擾亂 THE PRINCESS OF SNOW AND BLOOD","createTime":"2021-04-07T16:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T21:31:32.000Z","uid":28916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c081a5493d62a47214a86c5ada220979ffaa7802","tid":2479220,"uid":28916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeWzm2MN5GZhQ6AZtFT9f8BsgUBuNDwPaR9ezwjLt67wc?filename=sgTJGpV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgTJGpV.jpg&h=a426fb15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-STORY-<br />\n《擾亂 THE PRINCESS OF SNOW AND BLOOD》的故事背景設在明治 64 年，並由德川慶喜掌握權力的另一個日本。國家靠能量源「龍脈」，形成江戶和科學混合的獨特發展。但繁華背後，反體制派組織「蛇」正醞釀革命之火。德川政府委任闇組織「鵺」將其驅除。女主角-雪村咲羽在幼時被滅門，於是她作為「鵺」的處刑人，為報仇而持續尋找蛇埜目&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n-STAFF-<br />\n監督：工藤進<br />\nシリーズ構成：根津理香<br />\nキャラクターデザイン：小宮山楓乃<br />\nプロダクションデザイン：山口順<br />\n美術監督：安田ゆかり<br />\n色彩設計：赤間三佐子<br />\n撮影監督：小西庸平<br />\n編集：坂本雅紀<br />\n音響監督：今泉雄一<br />\n音楽：未知瑠<br />\n音響制作：ソニルード<br />\nアニメーション制作：BAKKEN RECORD<br />\n<br />\n-CAST-<br />\n雪村咲羽（ゆきむらさわ）：三森すずこ<br />\n月城真琴（つきしろまこと）：蒼井翔太<br />\n花風エレーナ（はなかぜえれーな）：Raychell<br />\n中村浅陽（なかむらあさひ）：伊藤彩沙<br />\n葛原仁（くずはらじん）：小林親弘<br />\n<br />\n-OP-<br />\nEXIST<br />\n歌：RAISE A SUILEN<br />\n<br />\n-ED-<br />\nEmbrace of light<br />\n歌：RAISE A SUILEN<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kUOOirFieao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkUOOirFieao&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=7504d940\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kUOOirFieao</a><br />\nOPED試聽<br />\n<br />\n-WEBSITE-<br />\n<a href=\"https://joran.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjoran.jp%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=2aed970a\" target=\"_blank\">https://joran.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n-PV-<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KdTZ-XQhFdE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKdTZ-XQhFdE&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=fa27d42c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KdTZ-XQhFdE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7JiVNXgTNnZWA36aZpgV0g8G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLxSscENEp7JiVNXgTNnZWA36aZpgV0g8G&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=b88d8f30\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7JiVNXgTNnZWA36aZpgV0g8G</a><br />\nAni-One 有得睇"},{"pid":"b51c88af356d00e66dc6cd73c1b20f801296f8c9","tid":2479220,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:14:21.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"6cab832c18c08b910d7700c4cec71f081ca14a67","tid":2479220,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T23:57:50.000Z","msg":"龍脈真係公廁設定..."},{"pid":"4fccab1025c866842d73691cd601b8cedc4b7b96","tid":2479220,"uid":62578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"係咪武士道既產品."},{"pid":"e98428870675bd605c580dba743e82d31ce7c480","tid":2479220,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"Why龍之子近年套套都咁老土"},{"pid":"03c7229d363941a330f72cdb332d96bbc4cd2782","tid":2479220,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"好看嗎..."},{"pid":"e69d9e51ed1aa0f0bd54ee285b78b424adc98cb3","tid":2479220,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T13:20:10.000Z","msg":"C9版鬼滅，暫時頭2集都OK"},{"pid":"57217d87a0528c065a23edca5cb0c80b35dbf0cf","tid":2479220,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T21:31:32.000Z","msg":"呢套嘢完全無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}